Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.80,0:00:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.27,0:00:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.81,0:00:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.92,0:00:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.13,0:00:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.93,0:00:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.21,0:01:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.65,0:01:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.32,0:01:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.96,0:01:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.66,0:01:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.64,0:01:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开地球的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.87,0:01:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民卫星的生活里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.74,0:01:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.61,0:01:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正义及和平为名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以压倒性的军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.72,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压制着各个殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.12,0:01:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战名称[流星作战]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.26,0:01:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和联合反目的部份卫星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定把伪装为流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.46,0:01:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.57,0:01:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这次作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已被联合总部发觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除我之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有人在破坏OZ的设施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想和大家见面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.65,0:02:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第七话\N[导致流血的剧本]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里是新爱德华基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭机也到达了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.37,0:02:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总共15部，数目很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.51,0:02:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道，辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.71,0:02:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经把OZ的所有高层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聚集在新爱德华基地这假情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,广泛流传开去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.45,0:02:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少我和你会出席是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己也是鱼饵吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备已100%完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.46,0:02:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不须再增加人手了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯在奈罗比吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点浪费了他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.23,0:03:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派驻奈罗比基地的OZ士兵很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.27,0:03:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里会变成激战区吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.47,0:03:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.28,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们就能毫不犹疑地献身给历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.98,0:03:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新爱德华，OZ会齐集那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦那家伙又失踪了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，但他说会再回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙总是自以为是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本来他被解雇也无话可说!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，解雇他很可惜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回来后我要好好教训他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.11,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦，你究竟想做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然独自去了别墅游玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也还是小孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身在我们这班污糟鬼之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.53,0:04:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也很累吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷打算留下我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,独自进行某项作战行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会?真的?队长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷担心我们的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,独自去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷\N岂不是有危险吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.55,0:04:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然不能白费\N卡特尔少爷的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我想卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事前我和商量一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旧金山市史丹利酒店吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想订房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个小孩没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们又见面了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的地看来一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会自己行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是，但互相帮助会更顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.47,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会更顺利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌袭啊!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌袭!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,货舱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.44,0:05:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，你也快点运进来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操纵就交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.92,0:06:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次的工作我绝对不想出错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶而一起工作无所谓吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙，还记着我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.54,0:06:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来会是一场激烈的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的明白吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.61,0:06:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次任务的重要性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是消灭OZ的绝佳机会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和以往不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次要收拾OZ这组织的首脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我就能回去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球圈统一联合\N新爱德华基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以最高司令官洛宾达元帅为首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,统领宇宙军的赛普提姆将军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球军的班迪将军等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.45,0:07:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合最高层的人齐集召开会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.46,0:07:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然，SMS(特务部队)的特列斯上级特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.93,0:07:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,副官蕾蒂‧安二级特校也会出席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.47,0:07:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯暗中向全世界散播假消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这会议不是联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.84,0:07:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是OZ的首脑齐集召开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历史会怎样推展呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.68,0:07:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会照特列斯大人你的决定推展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要看联合的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.92,0:07:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是否要纠正它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奈罗比基地要求和本编队联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉他们这是演习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会在蒙百沙上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.93,0:08:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行空中模拟战   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵，这次战斗会留下疑问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信杰克斯你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你命令说这攻击是必需的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.65,0:08:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合和OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.62,0:08:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使换过来了，世界也不会改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.62,0:08:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，为何要战斗? 杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面对世界各国的军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.93,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的抑制行动毕竟太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们现在需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非威吓世界的军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在军备扩张，新武器开发方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经不须再耗费努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是联合要行的正确之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.25,0:08:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换言之，是裁军吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裁军只是开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.78,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为最终一定要完全解除军备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错   班迪将军?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前我们曾经流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了实现统一的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.80,0:09:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那目的不知不觉地变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.87,0:09:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经要结束流血的时代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能结束就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.68,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，最近的一连串事件又如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.88,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用只有在宇宙才能炼制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.55,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹合金的机动战士的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球现在被那压倒性的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,置于危机之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.52,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实际战斗的SMS的何看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.63,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为那是\N殖民卫星的破坏活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合需要一名演员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.30,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我饰演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.11,0:09:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说出联合真正心意的角色吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你们明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.08,0:09:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星不信任我们是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了消除那种不信任感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.48,0:10:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们应该马上和他们开始对话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.96,0:10:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类的新历史要由对话开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不只是和卫星的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为也要和全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始相同的对话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.27,0:10:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N那些机动战士的问题…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果知道我们的和平意愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的破坏活动\N也就会失去意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.68,0:10:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谈判后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不见的路\N也会在我们面前出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.29,0:10:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,历史果然向错的方向推展吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.29,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要待最后的演员齐集后才开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.36,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为时代\N要朝着和平谈判前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帅!是敌袭!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这基地受到攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.67,0:10:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这防线很严密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十倍以上\N远超过想像中的数目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日不可退缩啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进攻须要太多时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有突击!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂，演员齐集了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.72,0:12:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也开幕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有命令开始[黎明行动]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，全体开始降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联络驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.96,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉他们我们想和卫星和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛宾达元帅!\N敌人已经展开攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样做时，这里的损毁会…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.17,0:13:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帅，现在先去避难较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.61,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.01,0:13:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也还想和卫星进行和平谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.15,0:13:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帅你就不能在这战斗里丧命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.99,0:13:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的讽刺我当听不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的确不想白白送死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了实现和平谈判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.83,0:13:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么请你使用\N我们的高速穿梭机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.79,0:13:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它能紧急出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.33,0:13:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你会想得\N这么周详和方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.10,0:13:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元帅，我也是联合的一份子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，那么拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，我来带路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.54,0:13:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭机在B12发射场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赛普提姆将军，请来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.09,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭机不是在那边吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.46,0:14:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以防万一，分散穿梭机是上策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我专用的穿梭机在F7机发射场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能载那么多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.73,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是SMS的最新机种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能出击的机动战士全部出击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人只是两部机!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令!\N菲亚柏基地有紧急通讯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.15,0:14:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是叛变!\N部份士兵正发起叛变!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界各地的基地正发生叛变!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.09,0:14:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.76,0:15:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曹长!不行!如果不投降…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.33,0:15:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别乱讲!你也是叛徒吗!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曹长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SMS的小鬼有何作为!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.18,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这基地已经被占领，投降吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叛徒给我住口!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就让你尝尝革命的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妄想!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请别冲动!诺茵特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建设是非常好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，为了建立那基础
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.21,0:15:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这未免流了太多血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，停止无益的反抗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们想尽量多招揽些同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的时代已经结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要由我们OZ亲手创立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和新秩序一起建立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也讲得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次政变是准备周详的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的士兵隐藏SMS的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派驻各地的联合军基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.81,0:16:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那也是\N联合军事组织的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.48,0:16:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的首脑受到毁灭性的打击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亚洲、欧洲、非洲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.09,0:16:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界的各个基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经被叛军占领了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛宾达元帅现在在哪里!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.59,0:16:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!查不到他的所在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.43,0:16:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟发生什么事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!一窝蜂涌出来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飞弹!?自己人也攻击吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人密集在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日不能警告你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.23,0:17:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我比较不利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.94,0:18:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ的新型机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们攻击联合啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两部机体和我们一模一样吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道他们也是…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁都好，阻碍的就要排除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那两部机体好相似啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么!?为何不快点出发?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛宾达元帅\N他们的穿梭机先出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们随后出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那部穿梭机!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.95,0:18:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是不幸的巧合!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不认为这是和平的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元…元师!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别冲动啊，年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.48,0:19:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.65,0:19:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛宾达元帅…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.56,0:19:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的飞弹招呼，多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次让我招呼你啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无意义的战斗你们还打不够吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.11,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.08,0:20:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们完全中了OZ的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开联合的宣传线路看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.35,0:20:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们把联合的和平支持者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部杀死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是卫星的宣战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.23,0:20:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们今日讨论和卫星和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.33,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堪称中心人物的洛宾达元帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.70,0:20:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不在人世
